  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Le Val Thorens is offered on a half board basis.</p>
<p>Buffet breakfast is served each morning 7.30 - 10am. </p>
<p><span>The hotel’s two restaurants offer two dining experiences and two different atmospheres. </span><span>La Fondue serves traditional specialties from Savoy, while Le Val Thorens Brasserie invites guests to savour a market-fresh menu that varies with the seasons. Le Val Thorens Brasserie is the main restaurant for breakfast and dinner, but bookings can also be made in La Fondue for dinner.</span><span></span></p>
<p><span>Bar 1971 is open for lunch with a snacking menu, crepes and a lovely terrace area with mountain views. </span></p>]]></cateringDescription>
