  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Comfort Village View Rooms</strong> are from 23m² to 26m² and can sleep up to 2 people. There's a double or twin beds <span>(please request at time of booking) and a view of the village.</span></p>
<p><strong>Comfort Piste View Rooms</strong> are the same as the above room type but with a view of the piste from the balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Family Piste View Rooms</strong> are from 23m² to 26m² and can sleep 2 adults and 1 child (under 12 years old). There's a double or twin beds <span>(please request at time of booking) and a single sofa bed. This room type has a view of the piste.</span></p>
